Package com.jprofiler.api.platform.descriptors

package com.jprofiler.api.platform.descriptors
Contains classes that represent different types of nodes in call trees.

See com.jprofiler.api.platform.connection for general remarks on the profiling platform and on how to use the JProfiler API
